What is Cloud Computing?
Imagine this...

Suppose you want to start a company.

To host your website, you need:

A server
Storage
Networking
Power
Cooling
Security

Buying all these costs lakhs of rupees.

Instead...

You rent everything from AWS.

This is called Cloud Computing.

Definition

Cloud Computing means renting IT resources (servers, storage, databases, networking, etc.) over the Internet instead of buying and maintaining them yourself.
